    "steam_appid": 3328270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328270/extras/3fb47fc14ce40ece8b22bb0326672778.avif?t=1769337710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328270/extras_big/3fb47fc14ce40ece8b22bb0326672778.avif?t=1769337710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>亵渎之牌</strong> 是一款以黑暗和神秘主义为主题的卡牌游戏，旨在实现愿望或带来死亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜者将是那位在三轮<strong>剪刀石头布</strong>中获胜，并成功召唤出正确的物品卡和特殊能力卡的人...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328270/extras/aff60e7764ecfff29bcb22aea9dab3d9.avif?t=1769337710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328270/extras_big/aff60e7764ecfff29bcb22aea9dab3d9.avif?t=1769337710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过召唤强大的物品卡和众多特殊能力卡，每一轮游戏既充满战略性，又带有随机性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;瘟疫医生&quot;带来光明与生命，而&quot;左轮手枪&quot;和&quot;上吊者&quot;则带来黑暗的诅咒与死亡...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328270/extras/bdef65b6fecd585b998727b8919eb5e6.avif?t=1769337710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328270/extras_big/bdef65b6fecd585b998727b8919eb5e6.avif?t=1769337710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带有<strong>钥匙符号</strong>的特殊能力卡则为游戏增添了更多深度和战略多样性。<br>例如，“诅咒镜子”能够抵挡邪恶鬼魂的攻击，并将其反弹回来。<br>而“占卜师的水晶球”则具备将光明带入隐秘之处的能力，并狡猾地短暂窥视另一张物品卡。<br>如果手中有“墓碑”，对方的存在必须暂停一轮...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论命运如何降临，记住遵守以下规则：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要在凌晨3点玩！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要在墓地玩！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永远要告别！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好面对来自阴间的骚乱并试试<strong>亵渎之牌</strong>吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你好运，勇敢的冒险者...</p>",
